Order can be maintained on an Imperial-controlled system against the wishes of the population through the use of garrisons.  Systems taken by force will require the presence of garrisons in order for us to maintain control.  Systems gained through Diplomacy or other non-military means will not require a garrison.  However, having troops stationed on each of our key systems will weaken the Rebel Alliance's ability to take those systems by assault.  Click on the Trooper Regiments tab on any of our systems' Defenses windows to see the number of trooper regiments ('Garrison Requirement') we need to maintain order.